::: {.intro}

I have a broad range of interests.  My areas of deeper expertise include algorithms, stochastic processes, and information theory.  Most (but not all . . .) of my work involves applying those kinds of techniques across various areas of Computer Science and related fields.  I have been lucky enough to find excellent collaborators in these many areas.

:::

